name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: No matter who you are, every eligible person should have an equal opportunity to exercise their right to vote. Legislation that restricts access to voting, especially for underrepresented voters, threatens the bedrock of our democracy. We must stand up against voter suppression.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: You can now order a Tempus #COVID19 test directly to your eligible patients' homes with our new at-home sample collection kit. Thank you to all the Tempus employees who contributed to this powerful and accessible testing option. Learn more below.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: The rise of Asian hate crimes, and the recent attack in Atlanta, is unacceptable. Here are a couple of valuable resources I've found: (1) @StopAAPIHate— tracks & responds to AAPI racist incidents; (2) @asianmhc— making mental health accessible to Asian communities. #StopAsianHate  https://t.co/g038JWtA8x

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: I had a great discussion with @SteveCase of @Revolution for @ExecClubChicago's Tech & Innovation Series about the need to support a collaborative start-up community and how to make data valuable, specifically for healthcare. Watch our conversation here:  https://t.co/p42ipMXTjf.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: I am thrilled to share Tempus ONE—a smart, voice-enabled portable device that brings @TempusLabs' platform and unparalleled multi-modal data library to life. Explore how Tempus ONE  brings #AI to the point-of-care (in beta today, launching broadly 2021):  https://t.co/ESmMopkhTa.  https://t.co/euAwPewVBR

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: It’s been a unique year, but I'm proud to share a few achievements from the @TempusLabs team: 800+ employees hired, 28 trial sites activated via #TIMETrial, 45 publications authored, >1M COVID tests ran, & hundreds of thousands of cancer samples sequenced.  https://t.co/H912g2iYaC  https://t.co/pkuC9WlNc9

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: On @GenomeWeb, I shared the progress of @TempusLabs’ infectious disease work, which includes our PCR #COVID19 diagnostic test as well as forthcoming tests, including a COVID at-home collection kit and an assay combining #influenza and SARS-CoV-2 testing:  https://t.co/piqsr139EH

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: I’m speaking with Axios’ @bryanrwalsh at @CBInsights’ virtual Future of Health event on Sept. 24 on the use of artificial intelligence in healthcare. Register today, and use my code TEMP300 for $300 off:  https://t.co/e0owVws64T.  #CBIFutureOfHealth #AI #AiInHealthcare

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: Tempus|N is bringing a data-driven approach to psychiatric treatment through #pharmacogenomic testing, which informs clinicians of their patients’ gene-drug interactions. Our aim is to bring precision medicine to psychiatric care:  https://t.co/uu9hNF2VvR.  https://t.co/vGAB5X36ZZ

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: The TIME Trial program and network is changing the clinical trial landscape. Our genomic profiling capabilities  coupled with our sponsor and site partners help bring targeted trials to patients in communities across the country. Read more on TIME here:  https://t.co/JvX1hK9XEp.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: I had a great conversation with Dr. @DavidAgus at FORTUNE @bstormhealth where we discussed how @TempusLabs is stratifying #COVID19+ patients by aggregating and structuring real-world data at scale. You can watch the full session here:  https://t.co/SSHD6Vw1Ze.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: Incredibly proud of the @TempusLabs team for their continued dedication to bringing the power of big data and artificial intelligence to healthcare, helping Tempus make No. 6 on this year's @CNBC #Disruptor50 list.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: The past few weeks have been nothing short of tragic. My heart goes out to George Floyd's family and those affected by racial inequality. We can no longer sit by and allow racism to run rampant. Be kind to yourselves and others. Listen, learn, support:  https://t.co/wbu3pIduLw.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: We now offer #COVID19 PCR testing at @TempusLabs. If you're an employer, hospital, oncologist, or institution looking for testing support, we can work with you to customize a program based on your company's unique testing needs for employees or patients:  https://t.co/c9oOAleShv.

name: Eric Lefkofsky
tweet: For #ASCO20, @TempusLabs published an abstract on our forthcoming #HRD test— a valuable tool that uses #genomicsequencing to help oncologists identify patients that may benefit from PARP inhibitor therapies.
